    <briefdescription>
<para>This file has the example usage of XSem_EbdLookUp API used to find whether a particular bit is essential or not. </para>    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This example is applicable for Versal SSIT devices and demonstrates the usage of look-up API for two SLRs. If the device has more no.of SLRs, You need to invoke the API by providing the corresponding XSem_EbdBufferX[] as an argument, where &apos;X&apos; refers to SLR ID.</para><para><preformatted>
MODIFICATION HISTORY:</preformatted></para><para><preformatted>Ver   Who   Date        Changes
